## The numbered spine
| # | Folder | Holds |
|---|--------|-------|
| 00 | engagement | charter, scope baseline + ledger, roles |
| 01 | intake | raw inputs (transcripts, notes) |
| 02 | deliverables | sprint-scoped team outputs |
| 03 | status | decision log, hours, tasks |
| 04 | client-surface | captain-approved, client-facing |
| 05 | personal | per-member private workspace |

## Conventions
Governance rules live in `.claude/rules/` (decision-log, frontmatter, publishing,
hours). Dynamic-workflow harnesses live in `.claude/skills/` — run `decision-audit`
before a close-out and `scope-creep` before a scope conversation.

